01:32:38.954 --> 01:32:40.754
Charlie!

01:33:57.733 --> 01:33:59.366
Giddup!

01:34:02.804 --> 01:34:04.704
Go get that son of a bitch!

01:34:42.778 --> 01:34:45.378
